overview: With the decline of the housing market, many of the agents quickly learn they must be ruthless in order to close a deal. Open houses promote open legs, and the clients always end up with a smile on their face. The steamy scenes include Alex Coal, Danni Rivers, Becky Bandini and Daphne Dare playing power games with Dava Foxx, Candice Dare, Gia Derza and Texas Patti exploring their sweet spots and driving each other into a sexual frenzy!
tagline: House hunting with a twist! Lesbians go on the hunt for each other!
title: Lesbian House Hunters 19
